Class Access

java.lang.Object
  com.bizosys.hsearch.filter.Access

public class Access
extends java.lang.Object

Currently access can be set by defining combination of

  • uid
  • team
  • role
  • org unit
  • orgunit + uid
  • orgunit + role
    • TODO:: Allow the regular expression here.
